科<br />\n咁一個星期就一個loop<br />\n數就日日都做d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6科"},{"pid":"d406f6c61776aaa237227e725f0dbafecbd99dca","tid":31644,"uid":40509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:27:54.000Z","msg":"我果時係study room 每日朝早8點温到夜晚6 7 點 反屋企食飯 係屋企 食完飯 沖完涼 温到12點前一定訓 唔會通頂 朝早7點幾一定要醒到 生理時鐘要較好 <br />\n同埋依家應該開始温 我果一有假期就用呢個timetable温書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0aaf2010c008bf31eed083f96e58681de74885","tid":31644,"uid":15080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:30:27.000Z","msg":"星期一 打丁<br />\n星期二打丁<br />\n星期三打丁<br />\n星期四打丁<br />\n星期五打丁<br />\n星期六打丁<br />\n星期日打兩次丁"},{"pid":"cceb7ba19ffc897bd5ab2f155ec628087acc2d7a","tid":31644,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:31:46.000Z","msg":"溫下書 打下機 出下街"},{"pid":"fcb48d1bec83aadb9ff2b3c20bcd050a1f17b84f","tid":31644,"uid":4206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我果時係study room 每日朝早8點温到夜晚6 7 點 <span style=\"color: red;\">反</span>屋企食飯 係屋企 食完飯 沖完涼 温到12點前一定訓 唔會通頂 朝早7點幾一定要醒到 生理時鐘要較好 <br />\n同埋依家應該開始温 我果一有假期就用呢個timetable温書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cc1579313cb1f769cd0edb80948a9839fe1739","tid":31644,"uid":34202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:43:35.000Z","msg":"嗰陣讀4+3+M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係倒轉考試順序嚟溫 清完一科就下一科 溫好書就做吓坊間啲mock paper或者ce al(睇你咩科而定 啱做先做 唔啱syllabus就唔好做混淆自己)<br />\n之後臨考幾日就做返dse past paper 畀自己一個大約嘅impression on題型<br />\n我就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a45ef29ca724300209d7bc448a831cc92a1522","tid":31644,"uid":34202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰陣讀4+3+M2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係倒轉考試順序嚟溫 清完一科就下一科 溫好書就做吓坊間啲mock paper或者ce al(睇你咩科而定 啱做先做 唔啱syllabus就唔好做混淆自己)<br />\n之後臨考幾日就做返dse past paper 畀自己一個大約嘅impression on題型<br />\n我就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n另外唔好溫到太夜 最好11點瞓7/8點起 唔使chur得咁盡 有時咪碌吓電話等陣再做過 但唔好hea得太耐 例如可能你溫3個鐘咪碌返15-20分鐘lihkg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f5d309db8c8a627dfa6d7d9698c2dd12a02ed9","tid":31644,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>星期一 打丁<br />\n星期二打丁<br />\n星期三打丁<br />\n星期四打丁<br />\n星期五打丁<br />\n星期六打丁<br />\n星期日打兩次丁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無丁"},{"pid":"0670e5763802ca80515ca3ae73026193cfa05001","tid":31644,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我果時係study room 每日朝早8點温到夜晚6 7 點 反屋企食飯 係屋企 食完飯 沖完涼 温到12點前一定訓 唔會通頂 朝早7點幾一定要醒到 生理時鐘要較好 <br />\n同埋依家應該開始温 我果一有假期就用呢個timetable温書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我驚我頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家最盡都係溫五個鐘一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a125e6741a5bda41d99d1f37111266dab818f2ce","tid":31644,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:53:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我果時係study room 每日朝早8點温到夜晚6 7 點 反屋企食飯 係屋企 食完飯 沖完涼 温到12點前一定訓 唔會通頂 朝早7點幾一定要醒到 生理時鐘要較好 <br />\n同埋依家應該開始温 我果一有假期就用呢個timetable温書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我驚我頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家最盡都係溫五個鐘一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n溫到投入嘅話日溫四粒鐘仲好過hea溫14粒鐘"},{"pid":"d5f97c94ddb49ec7903148554126bd9ccae44c87","tid":31644,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12